<template>
  <form action="" @submit.prevent="getUrl">
    <label for="urlName">Enter your url</label>
    <input type="text" name="urlName">

    <button type="submit">OK</button>

import axios from 'axios'

export default {
  name: 'App',

  methods: {
    getUrl() {
      axios
          .post('https://t.ly/api/v1/link/shorten', {
            api_token: 'Clo0A8CI9AF6PooLuaBdWc5yIf1uwF3WKBBXqONmY9MwqbXSzfD2wgsOwMBm',
            long_url: 'https://cerwyn.medium.com/build-api-authentication-with-laravel-passport-4ee047c11fd1',
            domain: 'https://t.ly/',
            include_qr_code: false
          })
          .then(res => {
            console.log(res.data)
          });
    }
  },
}
</script>
